            <title><![CDATA[CyclOps 0.2.0 release]]></title>
            <link>https://vectorinstitute.github.io/cyclops/blog/CyclOps-0.2.0-release</link>
            <guid>https://vectorinstitute.github.io/cyclops/blog/CyclOps-0.2.0-release</guid>
